{"tid":2011522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高銀金融以逾70億元出售啟德地皮","createTime":"2020-05-11T05:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T08:40:56.000Z","uid":128014,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"94d090feb0b0e92c2938dd7d35a6cdc0e234a8ec","tid":2011522,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:12:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525385-20200511.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525385-20200511.htm&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnySwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=708ffe38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525385-20200511.htm&h=aed26c63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525385-20200511.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n高銀金融公告指，向Top Family Group Limited出售啟德住宅地，總地盤面積約9708平方米，地基工程仍未展開。<br />\n<br />\n公告指，出售事項所得淨額約70.4億港元，擬用作償還借貸及一般營運資金。目前預期出售事項錄得虧損約25.71億元。<br />\n<br />\n集團表示，香港物業發展市場長遠仍存在不確定因素，考慮到有關物業處於初步發展階段及項目所需資金龐大，加上在物業市場前景不明朗及香港整體經濟低迷的背景下，董事採取審慎方針為集團的現有業務保留更多現金。"},{"pid":"9fb1fcbe2df28f237e9115135c1095b51e4671ad","tid":2011522,"uid":71508,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:20:01.000Z","msg":"都未用就賣？<br />\n靚地"},{"pid":"ecf6a8477827164bbfb1e7503f3dddfaa44789a6","tid":2011522,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:21:15.000Z","msg":"石禮謙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8bd31a07061d73456125fa141fea3ca74f4781","tid":2011522,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:23:19.000Z","msg":"嘩, 證明樓市又gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554e58672c2a61fcd1620651ef45419b1832feda","tid":2011522,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:24:04.000Z","msg":"樓市gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/s